{"tid":1982690,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"大種乞衣要人捐錢養貓，冇錢又要俾啲貓交配係乜玩法","createTime":"2020-04-21T10:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T09:33:45.000Z","uid":94799,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"35bd64f9d33f2741d9e994734f370be37d3e23bc","tid":1982690,"uid":94799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"呢個所謂大作家真係大種乞衣 領養兩隻唐貓翻嚟唔絕育<br />\n仲要刻意俾佢地交配 仲要影埋扑野過程出post<br />\n配種當時隻貓女一歲都唔夠 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦生咗一堆唐貓B出嚟 咁撚細個工作室前後加埋有9隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果宜家有隻貓有病 竟然話自己冇錢醫<br />\n要人捐錢救佢隻貓<br />\n屌！冇錢就唔好養咁多隻啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又開公司又做老闆 平時用個名氣賺左咁多水魚錢<br />\n仲好意思出嚟籌款？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最神奇係竟然有咁多人捐 啲中學雞既錢真係易昆！<br />\n<br />\n好心啦 講到咁冇能力咁窮<br />\n仲要俾啲唐貓生b究竟係撚野玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5hSvV4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5hSvV4A.png&h=2c342ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RF7S9pB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRF7S9pB.png&h=7d3e3699&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fpY4XX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fpY4XX.jpg&h=3c5b1425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b80209377ba97eaf31ca337a27260cdf704cdf04","tid":1982690,"uid":262246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"🌝十分認同！呢個作家完全顛覆左我對佢觀念，變相呃錢去滿足自己，炫耀自己，真係好噁心🤮。"},{"pid":"dedb1543fd9a43562a3dc2fcb3e3dead835d4e88","tid":1982690,"uid":320691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"其實醫生都話死亡率有9成，夾硬留隻貓係到隻貓唔係仲痛苦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca8e37d